In continuation of its strategy of business expansion in Africa, Vulkan Group had just concluded the opening of its subsidiary VULKAN AFRICA Ltd. to extend its industrial business in the whole continent. The company is also established in Johannesburg with a Distribution Center, Service Center and Sales and Application Engineering office. During the recent Mining Indaba Exhibition the company introduced to the market its new launches in Drive and Braking Systems Solutions, such as the New Power Supply for Electromagnetic Brakes V317, as well as its IoT and App-based solutions.